prompt: A hyper-detailed, photorealistic cinematic wide-angle shot at golden hour in a busy modern European city street that gently blends old stone buildings with modern glass offices. In the foreground, a stylish young woman with a natural, imperfect but attractive face, expressive eyes and subtle freckles is walking toward the camera. Her long hair is moving in the wind. She has neat bright red manicured nails on both hands. She wears a slightly wrinkled light beige trench coat, a dark turtleneck, a fitted black leather skirt, semi-transparent black tights and shiny black patent leather Dr. Martens ankle boots with clearly visible laces, stitching and glossy reflections. Around her, diverse pedestrians of different ages and ethnicities interact naturally: an elderly man with a cane, a woman pushing a stroller, a teenager on an electric scooter riding past, a man in a business suit looking at his smartphone, and a street musician playing a saxophone near a building entrance, with an open case containing a few visible coins and banknotes. Several pigeons are walking and flying low near the puddles on the wet pavement. Neon shop signs, billboards and street posters show clear, sharp Russian text in Cyrillic with different fonts and sizes (for example: «КИНОТЕАТР МИР», «ГОРОДСКАЯ БИБЛИОТЕКА», «МЕТРО», «КОФЕ & МЕЧТЫ»), some of them also reflected in shop windows and in the puddles on the ground. In the mid-ground, a detailed yellow tram with visible overhead power lines and pantograph is passing by. Next to it, several realistic cars are stopped at a traffic light, including a Chevrolet Tahoe 2008 (GMT900) in dark metallic color with recognizable boxy shape, chrome grille, roof rails and visible brand logo on the front, and a small red hatchback. The metal and glass surfaces of all vehicles show accurate reflections of the city, sky and lights. The Tahoe has a readable license plate with a few clear letters and numbers. The wet pavement reflects neon lights, car headlights and the warm sky; subtle puddles, small imperfections and texture of the asphalt are clearly visible. Far in the background, buildings and distant street details fade into light atmospheric haze under a partly cloudy sky with soft, warm sunlight. Depth of field is moderate: the main woman in the foreground is perfectly in focus (sharp eyes, realistic skin texture, visible fabric threads and leather grain), while pedestrians, cars and buildings in the background gradually become softer but still readable. High dynamic range, clean, crisp, ultra-detailed, no unwanted blur, no distortion, natural colors, realistic global illumination, 8K quality.
